<p>I made the trip on a bicycle. She answered the door wearing only a pair of white lace step-ins.<sup><a href="#footnote_13_97312" id="identifier_13_97312" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="Style of lingerie popular at the time. Coullottes basically.">xiv</a></sup> My erection was hard and instant.</p>
