Dumb bitch didn't even think to ask her, `why me, Mistress ?`, figure that shit out.">xxviii</a></sup></p>
<p>The dazzling edge on our orgies was dulling for me<sup><a href="#footnote_28_97312" id="identifier_28_97312" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="Gtfo, 18 yo straight out of the can ?!">xxix</a></sup>, but I was flipping Pepper with the techniques she had taught me. I knew all the buttons<sup><a href="#footnote_29_97312" id="identifier_29_97312" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="Again ?!">xxx</a></sup> to push for her, and she burned hotter than ever for her little puppy.</p>
<p>No wonder I was freaking for free, those Eastern pimps had charged her a fortune.</p>
<p>I tried one night to get a C note from her for a suit. I knew I had really come on fine in the bed. She had almost climbed the walls in her passion.</p>
<p>"Sugar," I said, "I saw a wild vine for a bill downtown. If you laid the scratch on me, I could cop tomorrow."</p>
<p>She slitted her green eyes and laughed in my face, and said, "Now listen Lil' Puppy, I don't give men money. I take it from them, and besides, as sweet as you are to this pussy, you don't need a suit. I like you as you are, with no clothes on at all."</p>
<p>I was a rank greenhorn, sure, but her cold turn down of my plea for the C note was bitchy cute, and I was a salty sucker, so I reacted like any stupid would-be pimp who had been Georgied.</p>
<p>I had fouled up basic business. I had led with my dick instead of my mitt.<sup><a href="#footnote_30_97312" id="identifier_30_97312" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="Hand.">xxxi</a></sup></p>
<p>I reached down and slapped her hard against the side of her face. It sounded like a pistol shot. On impact a thrill shot through me. I should have slugged her with a baseball bat.<sup><a href="#footnote_31_97312" id="identifier_31_97312" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="No dumbass, you should've ordered her on her knees, bubblin' dat butt out, and worn your belt down on her a few layers. Wtf.">xxxii</a></sup></p>
<p>The bitch uncoiled from that bed like a striking yellow cobra, hooked her arms around my waist and sank her razor sharp teeth into my navel.</p>
<p>The shock paralyzed me. I fell on my back across the bed moaning in pain. I could feel blood rolling from the wound down toward my crotch, but I couldn't speak. I couldn't move.<sup><a href="#footnote_32_97312" id="identifier_32_97312" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="Holy shit this nigga's worthless in a fight.">xxxiii</a></sup></p>
