Pshaw.">xlvii</a></sup> She had called the drug store twice just before closing. She had made licking and sucking sounds to get me out to her place. I made excuses and put her off. I wondered at the time why I was so important when she was a douche bag<sup><a href="#footnote_47_97312" id="identifier_47_97312" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="I had no idea this expression's over half a century old. I had figured it a relatively recent innovation of the Important Barristas Union. Then again, `manchild` is also older than the 90s... I guess I'ma have to confront the cold hard facts of the matter : that crowd isn't either creative or relevant enough to actually coin terminology.">xlviii</a></sup> for that mob that was laying it into her.</p>
